                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ul>
                    <li>Provide an authentication system for staff and students</li>
                    <li>Allow staff to easily manage student accounts and other staff accounts</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="one-third column">
                <a href="{{ url_for('auth.login') }}" class="button larger primary mt-1">
